{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"4801","heading":"Congressional findings and declaration of purpose","label":"4801 Congressional findings and declaration of purpose","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/ch79","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4801","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","Effective Date, , , provided that:Pub. L. 99–198, title XVI, § 163199 Stat. 1622Dec. 23, 1985“This subtitle [subtitle B (§§ 1611–1631) of title XVI of , enacting this chapter] shall become effective on .”Pub. L. 99–198January 1, 1986","Short Title, , , provided that:Pub. L. 99–198, title XVI, § 161199 Stat. 1606Dec. 23, 1985“This subtitle [subtitle B (§§ 1611–1631) of title XVI of , enacting this chapter] may be cited as the ‘Pork Promotion, Research, and Consumer Information Act of 1985’.”Pub. L. 99–198"],"amendments":["Effective Date, , , provided that:Pub. L. 99–198, title XVI, § 163199 Stat. 1622Dec. 23, 1985“This subtitle [subtitle B (§§ 1611–1631) of title XVI of , enacting this chapter] shall become effective on .”Pub. L. 99–198January 1, 1986","Short Title, , , provided that:Pub. L. 99–198, title XVI, § 161199 Stat. 1606Dec. 23, 1985“This subtitle [subtitle B (§§ 1611–1631) of title XVI of , enacting this chapter] may be cited as the ‘Pork Promotion, Research, and Consumer Information Act of 1985’.”Pub. L. 99–198"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":null,"label":"a","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4801%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4801%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"pork and pork products are basic foods that are a valuable and healthy part of the human diet;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4801%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4801%2Fa%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"produced by thousands of producers, including many small- and medium-sized producers; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4801%2Fa%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"consumed by millions of people throughout the United States on a daily basis;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4801%2Fa%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"pork and pork products must be available readily and marketed efficiently to ensure that the people of the United States receive adequate nourishment;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4801%2Fa%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a/4/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a/4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4801%2Fa%2F4%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the welfare of pork producers and persons concerned with producing and marketing pork and pork products; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a/4/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a/4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4801%2Fa%2F4%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the general economy of the United States;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":null,"label":"5","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4801%2Fa%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"pork and pork products move in interstate and foreign commerce;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"6","heading":null,"label":"6","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a/6","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4801%2Fa%2F6","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"pork and pork products that do not move in such channels of commerce directly burden or affect interstate commerce in pork and pork products; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"7","heading":null,"label":"7","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a/7","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4801%2Fa%2F7","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"in recent years, increasing quantities of low-cost, imported pork and pork products have been brought into the United States and replaced domestic pork and pork products in normal channels of trade.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":null,"label":"b","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4801%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4801%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/b/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4801%2Fb%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"strengthen the position of the pork industry in the marketplace; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/b/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4801%2Fb%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"maintain, develop, and expand markets for pork and pork products.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4801%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Such procedure shall be implemented, and such program shall be conducted, at no cost to the Federal Government.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4801%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/b/3/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/b/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4801%2Fb%2F3%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"permit or require the imposition of quality standards for pork or pork products;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/b/3/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/b/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4801%2Fb%2F3%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"provide for control of the production of pork or pork products; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/b/3/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4801/b/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4801%2Fb%2F3%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"otherwise limit the right of an individual pork producer to produce pork and pork products.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}]}
